channel.title: Paying to help me make a server
channel.description:
Ok i'm seriously confused about making a server, i tried for 3 hours using a guide on "making you're on server"
so if anyone asks me now "did you do this" "did you do that" the answer will probably be "i don't know :S"
If someone would take me step by step from step 1 i'd happily make them admin (when i find out how to) and pay them 4m rs cash.[br][size=1]Posted at: November 01, 2006, 05:58:15 AM[/size][hr]i would obviously perfer someone who has allready made their own server and prehaps let me check it out if thats ok.
